casebody.head_matter:
ELIM ROMANIAN PENTECOSTAL CHURCH, et al., Applicants,
v.
J.B. PRITZKER, Governor of Illinois.
No. 19A1046.
Supreme Court of the United States.
May 29, 2020
Application for injunctive relief presented to Justice Kavanaugh and by him referred to the Court denied. The Illinois Department of Public Health issued new guidance on May 28. The denial is without prejudice to Applicants filing a new motion for appropriate relief if circumstances warrant.
